### **Integration Files:**
```
lib-liveeditor/
  └── ComponentsList.tsx                  ← Component registry

componentsStructure/
  └── index.ts                            ← Export all structures

context/editorStoreFunctions/
  └── index.ts                            ← Export all functions
```

